### Delete Gig (Owner Client Only)
# ✅ Should return 200 + "Gig deleted successfully" if owner
# ❌ Should return 403 if different client's token
# ❌ Should return 401 if no token provided
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/gigs/6a3e769baad78ded4c724688
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjZhM2U3NTViYWFkNzhkZWQ0YzcyNDY4MCIsImlhdCI6MTc4MjQ3ODMyNywiZXhwIjoxNzgzMDgzMTI3fQ.MJyI1-BytjP92qDUlQ-lT4E_3cL-8blo4wSWa6uRS0I